"the men's event\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"the 18th Paralympic gold\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"atParis2024\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain's most successfulParalympianovercame a 7.18 seconds deficit at the only mid-race checkpoint to stretch her record-breaking exploits in the eastern suburbs of theFrenchcapital.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 7.18 seconds deficit\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"the only mid-race checkpoint\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"her record-breaking exploits\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 675}, {\"ngram\": \"the eastern suburbs\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"theFrenchcapital\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the 46-year-old was delighted with her latest triumph, she bemoaned a missed opportunity for disability sport and raised the issue of gender inequality after completing a course of just 14.1 kilometres in 20 minutes and 22.15 seconds.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her latest triumph\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"a missed opportunity\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"disability sport\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"gender inequality\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"a course\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"just 14.1 kilometres\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"20 minutes\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"22.15 seconds\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Storey said riders had appealed to organisers about the race length before the Games but not received a response.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Storey\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"riders\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"the race length\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"a response\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's C5 event, in which Britain's Blaine Hunt finished 11th, was double the distance, comprising two laps of the same course.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cervical_vertebrae\", \"score\": 0.9991810337058695, \"rank\": 0.0008196373813674818, \"text\": \"C5\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\", \"Q265868\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cervical_vertebrae\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cervical_vertebrae\"}, {\"begin\": 1117, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blaine_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.9952647894118013, \"rank\": 0.004757739486537487, \"text\": \"Blaine\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blaine_Anderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blaine_Anderson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"two laps\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"the same course\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the shortest Paralympic time trial we have ever had,\\\" said Storey, who was 4.69 secs quicker than France's Heidi Gaugain.\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1317, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.742045322025147, \"rank\": 0.34650934959304497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1326, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\", \"score\": 0.9999999934216248, \"rank\": 5.123988768524208e-09, \"text\": \"Heidi\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shortest Paralympic time trial\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"Storey\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think it's a real shame because you do not get to showcase Para sport in the way that you want to.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a real shame\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"Para sport\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I hope this is the only time it's less than 20k.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only time\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"20k\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to ask the organisers (why it was so short).\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really hope that they never do this to the women again because I think it's been appalling \\\"But there is plenty of time in the day for us to do two laps like the men.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1689}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"two laps\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And having fought so hard for parity in women's cycling, to not have it in Para cycling after what we had in Glasgow (world championships) last year is a real disappointment.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999417714224, \"rank\": 5.8170226402214505e-08, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parity\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"women's cycling\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"Para cycling\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"(world championships\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"a real disappointment\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had to put that disappointment aside and just concentrate on what I can control because I could not control the race distance.\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that disappointment\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"the race distance\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I really hope that they never do this to the women again because I think it's been appalling.\\\"\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The PA news agency understands organisers opted to hold some time trials over the shorter distance due to there being 19 races on Wednesday's busy schedule, in addition to medal ceremonies.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The PA news agency\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"some time trials\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"the shorter distance\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"19 races\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday's busy schedule\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"medal ceremonies\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Storey wrote her name in the history books at Tokyo 2020 by claiming a trio of titles to move ahead of former swimmer Mike Kenny in the all-time list of GB athletes.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2377, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6279320425767224, \"rank\": 0.592130540772866, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Kenny_(writer)\", \"score\": 0.8376701868197467, \"rank\": 0.1937799043061952, \"text\": \"Mike Kenny\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Kenny_(writer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Kenny_(writer)\"}, {\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9005793856669296, \"rank\": 0.11034795669647371, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Storey\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"the history books\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"a trio\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"former swimmer\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-time list\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The time trial inJapanwas held over a distance of 24km.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The time trial\"