08_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Storey's victory\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"13 races\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"her overall Paralympic medal tally\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(I am) on top of the world,\\\" she said.\\\"\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I came here to try and get the gold medal (in this event) for the fifth time, fourth defence and I have done it.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3332}, {\"ngram\": \"the fifth time\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the perfectly-paced ride.\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the perfectly-paced ride\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was down seven seconds at the first time check, but I knew that was the easiest part of the course going into that first time check because there were quite a few descents and technical sections where you can get free speed, have a recovery and be prepared for that first climb.\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time check\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"the easiest part\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3510}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3524}, {\"ngram\": \"that first time check\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3557}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a few descents\", \"from\": 35